room_title: Escape room "When the Clock Strikes Twelf" by MindScape in Somerset
room_address: 110 Richie Lane, Suite C Somerset, KY 42503
room_description: The abominable snowman has ravaged the toy factory at the north pole! Will your team of elves be able to repair Santa's toy factory before the clock strikes twelve? While this game is especially family friendly, the gameplay is still awesome for adults!
